comments: Grant (POR) moves alongside Johnson's (SAS) path and absorbs marginal body contact during the driving shot attempt.
Sochan (SAS) brings his arm toward Lillard's (POR) path and marginal contact occurs before Lillard releases away during the drive.
Lillard (POR) goes to, not through, Sochan's (SAS) space and marginal contact occurs as Lillard releases away during the drive.
Hart (POR) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Johnson (SAS) during the drive.
Johnson (SAS) avoids making contact with Hart (POR) during his driving shot attempt.
Simons (POR) momentarily grasps Poeltl's (SAS) left arm before releasing and marginal contact occurs off-ball.
Johnson (SAS) and Lillard (POR) engage in marginal arm to arm contact while reaching for the rebound.
Jones (SAS) brings his arm toward Simons' (POR) path and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Sochan (SAS) makes clean contact with the ball during Lillard's (POR) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Sochan (SAS) commits a take foul on Simons (POR).
